import React from "react"; const Experience = () => { return (

experience

{/*Linkway Software Solutions */}

2023 July - Present

Software Developer, Linkway Software Solutions

Building "Easy Stock Taker," a new Flutter mobile application.
Designing, developing, testing, and documenting UI designs for aesthetically pleasing screens.
Reviewing code and ensuring quality.

{" "}
{/* DX mail Admin */}

2023 Oct - Present

Admin and Database Support, DX mail (Freightways),

Maintain nationwide databases for data analysis, conduct data integrity audits and resolve issues.
Acquire, process, cleanse, and upload data from various sources.
Develop national reports, dashboards, and SQL procedures.
Implement data visualization for dashboards.
Support recruitment tasks and assist in company-wide projects.
Import and transfer data to secure central database.

{" "}
{/* DX mail Machine Operator */}

2023 Feb - 2023 Oct

Machine Operator/ Data Assistant, DX mail (Freightways)

Data entry for video encoding and billing information.
Route mapping, mail processing, forklift operation, machinery setup, operation, and maintenance.
Street delivery network management, quality control, recordkeeping, and error reporting for outbound mail sorting. Maintains logs and records of mail produced.

{" "}
{/* Halza software Solution (I) Pvt Ltd */}

2021 July - 2022 Oct

Front End Developer, Halza Software Solution LLC

Front-end web development and support for HALZA's digital health solution in an agile environment.
Implement practical technical solutions for product discovery and business development.
Collaborate with the product development team to align solutions with existing architecture.
Perform quality reviews, deploy updates, and provide simple technical workarounds.
Contribute to internal process development for increased efficiency and stability.
Implement translations, caching strategy, iframe, PWA, and SignalR.

{" "}
{/* Three Phase Techno Solution (I) Pvt Ltd */}

2020 June - 2021 June

Development Engineer, Three Phase Techno Solution (I) Pvt Ltd

Full-stack web application development in an agile environment.{" "}
Ensured responsive, accessible UI for optimal user experience.
Created custom data visualization plugins using React.js, HTML, and CSS.

{" "}
{/* Ashtec Contractors Pvt Ltd */}

2015 Mar - 2016 Dec

Junior Web Developer, Babte Technologies Pvt Ltd

Developed the front end of the entire website using HTML5, CSS3, jQuery, JSON, Ajax and JavaScript
Converted raw images and layouts from a graphic designer in to CSS/HTML/SVG themes.
Created dynamic webpage using API calls.

{/* Babte Technologies Pvt Ltd */}

2014 Sep - 2015 Mar

Software Engineer Trainee, Babte Technologies Pvt Ltd

Participated in designing and developing of various applications using ASP.NET
Wrote SQL queries, stored procedures and transaction queries..
